SubjectRegulations Amending the Motor Vehicle Safety Regulations (Standard 216 — Roof Crush Resistance and Standard 220 — Rollover Protection)
PrecisREGULATIONS AMENDING THE MOTOR VEHICLE SAFETY REGULATIONS (Standard 216 - Roof Crush Resistance and Standard 220 - Rollover Protection) to improve the safety of vehicle occupants in the event of a vehicle rollover and to maintain harmonization with safety standards recently proposed by the United States.
